Account

post.description:
This endpoint runs the Vault calculation specified in the POST body parameters.
It can take one or more units as input.

Remarks:

*   Start and and end date must be within the configuration's min and max date range

parameters.name: X-FactSet-Api-Long-Running-Deadline
parameters.description: Long running deadline in seconds when only one unit is passed in the POST body.

200.description: Expected response, if the calculation has one unit and is completed with an error.

schema.description: FactSet's request key header.

X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key.description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only available after successful authentication.
